1
00:00:10,860 --> 00:00:12,780
♪The wind blows, but I don't see you♪

2
00:00:12,820 --> 00:00:14,740
♪I added a few more strokes♪

3
00:00:14,740 --> 00:00:17,380
♪To the ending♪

4
00:00:17,580 --> 00:00:21,580
♪With the flowers falling
and the time passing♪

5
00:00:21,860 --> 00:00:24,140
♪Leaving only memories behind♪

6
00:00:24,300 --> 00:00:28,220
♪The wind blows from a long distance♪

7
00:00:28,340 --> 00:00:31,020
♪Yet, you didn't show up♪

8
00:00:31,140 --> 00:00:33,140
♪This love is full of regrets♪

9
00:00:33,300 --> 00:00:37,420
♪You are but a dream
in this fleeting life♪

10
00:00:40,260 --> 00:00:41,260
[Part For Ever]

11
00:00:41,260 --> 00:00:42,000
[Adapted from the novel by Jing Mo,]

12
00:00:42,000 --> 00:00:42,900
[My Lord,
Madam Doesn't Want to See You Again]

13
00:00:42,900 --> 00:00:44,780
[Episode 17]

14
00:00:47,880 --> 00:00:49,710
Fragrance lingers around the banks,

15
00:00:50,520 --> 00:00:52,350
and lotus leaves cover the pond.

16
00:00:53,960 --> 00:00:56,350
It's a pity that flowers bloom
only to wither away.

17
00:00:57,110 --> 00:00:58,840
If only we could preserve them.

18
00:00:59,350 --> 00:01:00,560
I will preserve them for you.

19
00:02:00,710 --> 00:02:03,640
It's a pity that flowers bloom
only to wither away.

20
00:02:05,000 --> 00:02:06,680
If only we could preserve them.

21
00:02:23,540 --> 00:02:26,420
♪The lush and fragrant grass
made longing hard to endure♪

22
00:02:26,580 --> 00:02:29,940
♪Can I entrust my heart to you?♪

23
00:02:29,940 --> 00:02:32,060
[Lotus Rouge]

24
00:02:32,980 --> 00:02:36,300
♪On the path of emotions♪

25
00:02:36,460 --> 00:02:40,100
♪Reflected in a mirror
by moonlight through a window♪

26
00:02:40,340 --> 00:02:43,060
♪How much is your affection?♪

27
00:02:43,220 --> 00:02:49,340
♪When the time to love is not right,
worldly matters make it hard to endure♪

28
00:02:49,380 --> 00:02:52,060
♪Amid all worldly matters,
I only devote to one person♪

29
00:02:52,140 --> 00:02:56,900
♪Love is silent, but it leaves traces
as deep as the sea♪

30
00:02:56,980 --> 00:03:02,700
♪I accompany you
for a part of the journey♪

31
00:03:02,780 --> 00:03:05,180
♪Our longing for each other
guides us through countless lives♪

32
00:03:05,260 --> 00:03:10,300
♪The flowers of the entire city
blossom for a person♪

33
00:03:10,580 --> 00:03:15,620
♪Let's spend
the rest of our lives together♪

34
00:03:30,400 --> 00:03:31,240
You've actually

35
00:03:31,470 --> 00:03:33,150
prepared the same thing as me.

36
00:03:33,910 --> 00:03:35,080
It's as if

37
00:03:35,240 --> 00:03:36,590
we're of one mind.

38
00:03:42,360 --> 00:03:43,520
There was only a little time.

39
00:03:43,840 --> 00:03:44,840
Please don't mind if it's not perfect.

40
00:03:57,660 --> 00:04:03,620
♪People sit silently
by candlelight as night begins♪

41
00:04:07,310 --> 00:04:09,030
You must have put
a lot of effort into it.

42
00:04:09,590 --> 00:04:10,840
Your eyes look tired.

43
00:04:12,000 --> 00:04:13,310
I'm just glad you like it.

44
00:04:15,310 --> 00:04:16,750
I prepared a gift for you too.

45
00:04:21,780 --> 00:04:27,460
♪You turn back to ascend the stage
wearing a green robe♪

46
00:04:27,660 --> 00:04:33,220
♪A song asking about heart matters,
but who will answer?♪

47
00:04:33,660 --> 00:04:39,020
♪An old dream with infatuation
and resentment and complications♪

48
00:04:39,060 --> 00:04:40,460
♪You sing for me♪

49
00:04:40,540 --> 00:04:44,500
♪In the play,
telling of separations and reunions♪

50
00:04:44,540 --> 00:04:50,420
♪Pear blossoms fall
and flowing sleeves feel like yesterday♪

51
00:04:54,000 --> 00:04:54,920
This way,

52
00:04:55,160 --> 00:04:56,240
I can preserve

53
00:04:57,120 --> 00:04:58,360
these lotus flowers for you.

54
00:04:59,660 --> 00:05:03,220
♪Amid the applause,
who can see through it?♪

55
00:05:03,700 --> 00:05:08,740
♪Aren't the characters
in the play you and me?♪

56
00:05:12,000 --> 00:05:12,830
Let me help you.

57
00:05:18,360 --> 00:05:20,430
If you mess it up, you'll be in trouble.

58
00:05:21,620 --> 00:05:27,540
♪Going through the ups and downs of life,
living like a carefree crane♪

59
00:05:27,660 --> 00:05:33,420
♪In a moment of reminiscence,
how can one resist the beauty of spring♪

60
00:05:36,600 --> 00:05:37,390
What do you think?

61
00:05:37,830 --> 00:05:39,040
Am I in trouble?

62
00:05:41,600 --> 00:05:42,430
Yes.

63
00:05:49,560 --> 00:05:51,190
If that's how you're going to punish me,

64
00:05:51,830 --> 00:05:53,190
then from now on,

65
00:05:53,310 --> 00:05:54,630
I'll do your makeup every day.

66
00:05:56,620 --> 00:05:59,540
♪This life is filled
with too much affection♪

67
00:05:59,660 --> 00:06:03,220
♪Amid the applause,
who can see through it?♪

68
00:06:03,620 --> 00:06:08,260
♪Aren't the characters
in the play you and me?♪

69
00:06:08,540 --> 00:06:14,300
♪Pear blossoms fall
and flowing sleeves feel like yesterday♪

70
00:06:14,460 --> 00:06:19,780
♪The heart is closed,
unable to gaze at the emotional eyes♪

71
00:06:20,920 --> 00:06:21,480
Wan'er,

72
00:06:21,950 --> 00:06:22,800
what's wrong?

73
00:06:24,360 --> 00:06:25,830
I'm just feeling a little dizzy.

74
00:06:26,360 --> 00:06:27,270
I'll be fine.

75
00:06:28,160 --> 00:06:30,190
Come on, let's go home.

76
00:06:41,830 --> 00:06:43,070
I'm just a little tired.

77
00:06:43,070 --> 00:06:44,310
I can walk.

78
00:06:44,750 --> 00:06:46,190
You need rest if you're tired.

79
00:06:46,560 --> 00:06:47,830
I'm really fine.

80
00:07:08,750 --> 00:07:09,920
If you don't lie down,

81
00:07:09,920 --> 00:07:10,830
I'll kiss you again

82
00:07:10,830 --> 00:07:13,270
until you listen to me.

83
00:07:14,480 --> 00:07:15,270
Fine, fine.

84
00:07:15,680 --> 00:07:17,070
I will close my eyes and get some rest.

85
00:07:44,070 --> 00:07:45,830
You exhausted yourself

86
00:07:46,950 --> 00:07:48,430
just to prepare the sachet for me.

87
00:08:36,750 --> 00:08:37,670
Commander Zhao.

88
00:08:39,390 --> 00:08:41,080
Ling Xiao, you despicable man,

89
00:08:41,440 --> 00:08:43,390
you've done nothing but dirty deeds.

90
00:08:46,440 --> 00:08:48,320
You're masked assassins.

91
00:08:48,360 --> 00:08:49,550
Who's the one

92
00:08:49,870 --> 00:08:50,870
doing dirty deeds here?

93
00:08:51,080 --> 00:08:52,910
You sent your men
to hunt me down secretly.

94
00:08:53,750 --> 00:08:55,000
That's so despicable.

95
00:08:57,240 --> 00:08:58,840
Falling into your hands today,

96
00:08:59,200 --> 00:09:00,600
I have nothing more to say.

97
00:09:01,790 --> 00:09:04,080
My sworn brother, I'm useless.

98
00:09:04,600 --> 00:09:06,080
I failed to save Wan'er.

99
00:09:06,580 --> 00:09:09,500
I'll apologize to you
when I see you in the netherworld.

100
00:09:09,600 --> 00:09:10,390
Hanfeng.

101
00:09:13,270 --> 00:09:14,150
For the sake

102
00:09:14,150 --> 00:09:15,510
of your unwavering loyalty to Wan'er,

103
00:09:16,000 --> 00:09:17,200
I'll spare you this time.

104
00:09:23,480 --> 00:09:25,870
My Lord, are you really going
to release a threat?

105
00:09:26,360 --> 00:09:27,480
With his skills,

106
00:09:27,840 --> 00:09:29,870
even if he trains for another ten years,
he won't be able to get close to me.

107
00:09:30,840 --> 00:09:31,630
However,

108
00:09:31,870 --> 00:09:34,200
what he said about me hunting
him down was a little strange.

109
00:09:34,960 --> 00:09:37,200
Send the Shadow Guards
to keep an eye on him.

110
00:09:37,270 --> 00:09:38,080
Yes, My Lord.

111
00:10:12,750 --> 00:10:13,320
How are you feeling?

112
00:10:13,750 --> 00:10:14,600
Are you still feeling dizzy?

113
00:10:15,960 --> 00:10:17,720
It's probably because I'm hungry.

114
00:10:19,240 --> 00:10:20,080
I heard

115
00:10:20,480 --> 00:10:21,670
you really like the snow crab bucket

116
00:10:21,670 --> 00:10:22,630
from Qinghe Restaurant.

117
00:10:22,870 --> 00:10:23,870
How about

118
00:10:23,870 --> 00:10:25,120
I'll take you there tomorrow?

119
00:10:25,480 --> 00:10:27,790
That's the most famous restaurant
in Canglong City.

120
00:10:27,840 --> 00:10:29,480
We have to make a reservation
in advance.

121
00:10:30,270 --> 00:10:31,630
Let alone a restaurant,

122
00:10:32,270 --> 00:10:34,000
even if you want the stars in the sky,

123
00:10:35,790 --> 00:10:37,080
I'll get them for you.

124
00:10:38,390 --> 00:10:39,480
In that case,

125
00:10:39,480 --> 00:10:41,120
I must dress up

126
00:10:41,480 --> 00:10:43,080
to match your kind gesture.

127
00:10:43,100 --> 00:10:46,420
♪Putting on makeup as the bright moon
scattered its light on the sky♪

128
00:10:46,460 --> 00:10:49,340
♪Like white frost♪

129
00:10:49,980 --> 00:10:51,620
[Liu's Joss Paper]

130
00:10:52,170 --> 00:10:54,110
Candied Haws!

131
00:10:54,280 --> 00:10:56,670
Sweet and sour Candied Haws!

132
00:10:56,670 --> 00:10:57,550
Try this.

133
00:11:01,390 --> 00:11:02,200
And this.

134
00:11:03,440 --> 00:11:05,000
Don't just serve me.

135
00:11:05,840 --> 00:11:06,670
You should try them too.

136
00:11:09,020 --> 00:11:11,500
♪I was a youth when I started writing♪

137
00:11:11,540 --> 00:11:15,660
♪Falling in love,
there are too many deep memories♪

138
00:11:17,630 --> 00:11:18,670
Qinghe Restaurant's food

139
00:11:19,270 --> 00:11:21,440
isn't as delicious
as the rumors suggest.

140
00:11:23,080 --> 00:11:24,480
Try this now.

141
00:11:24,750 --> 00:11:25,720
Snow crab bucket.

142
00:11:26,180 --> 00:11:29,460
♪Split the word "love" in two lines♪

143
00:11:32,670 --> 00:11:34,320
You're teasing me again.

144
00:11:35,900 --> 00:11:38,340
♪I was a youth when I started writing♪

145
00:11:38,380 --> 00:11:42,540
♪Falling in love,
there are too many deep memories♪

146
00:11:43,180 --> 00:11:45,260
♪When I stopped writing,
I was the only one aware♪

147
00:11:47,870 --> 00:11:49,150
I want to try

148
00:11:49,320 --> 00:11:50,080
the soup too.

149
00:11:53,060 --> 00:11:56,300
♪Split the word "love" in two lines♪

150
00:11:56,620 --> 00:12:01,980
♪But when it's written down,
it's hard to make it whole♪

151
00:12:04,550 --> 00:12:05,360
My Lord.

152
00:12:12,600 --> 00:12:14,630
Do you have something to do?

153
00:12:17,870 --> 00:12:18,510
Enjoy the food.

154
00:12:19,000 --> 00:12:19,870
I'll be right back.

155
00:13:39,860 --> 00:13:45,380
♪The lone snowy peak
is unable to reach the moon♪

156
00:13:45,540 --> 00:13:52,060
♪Gatherings and partings are fated,
love also has its sorrow or joy♪

157
00:13:52,620 --> 00:13:56,540
♪My concern
sinks into the long night♪

158
00:13:56,660 --> 00:14:00,580
♪May I be bold to ask what love means?♪

159
00:14:00,620 --> 00:14:06,380
♪In the flickering candlelight,
I dream of a glimpse of her♪

160
00:14:06,820 --> 00:14:10,220
♪In my dreams,
the past remains unchanged♪

161
00:14:10,300 --> 00:14:13,780
♪In my lifetime, sorrows
and joys become a book♪

162
00:14:13,820 --> 00:14:20,020
♪I write the rest of my life
with one stroke♪

163
00:14:20,940 --> 00:14:24,300
♪The morning is full of joy♪

164
00:14:24,380 --> 00:14:28,300
♪The evening is full of melancholy♪

165
00:14:28,380 --> 00:14:34,580
♪Miss you a lifetime
with love engraved in my bones♪
